'''Repabliki ya Cameroon''' goba '''Cameroon''' ke naga lefasaneng la [[Afrika]]. Cameroon e bogare bodikela ba [[Afrika]], e wela seleteng sa [[Bogare ba Afrika|Bogare Ba Afrika]].

Cameroon e agišane le :
* [[Nigeria]] (bodikela),
* [[Chad]] (lebia bohlabela),
* [[Central African Republic]] (bohlabela),
* [[Equatorial Guinea]] (borwa),
* [[Gabon]] (borwa),
* [[Republic ya Congo]] (borwa).

